Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.13,0:00:04.47,Narration Off,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}Encounters are mysterious!\NBut cases are even more so!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.47,0:00:06.60,Narration Off,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}I'm so glad I'm with you!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.60,0:00:10.04,Narration Off,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}Today's title is a bit unusual!\NCan you solve the mystery in Part 1?!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.04,0:00:11.61,Narration Off,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}He sees the single truth for what it is,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.61,0:00:13.65,Narration Off,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}and looks like a kid but has the mind of an adult.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.65,0:00:16.22,Narration Off,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}His name? Detective Conan!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.59,0:01:47.42,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Mitsuhiko.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.42,0:01:51.43,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Is there really an empty lot nearby where we can play baseball?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.43,0:01:53.59,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,There is!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.59,0:01:57.76,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}C'mon, you guys. Play soccer once in a while, will ya?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.27,0:02:02.30,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,We're here!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.30,0:02:03.30,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.30,0:02:05.51,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,What do you mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.51,0:02:07.03,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Right here!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.55,0:02:19.79,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,This is a construction site for an apartment building!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.79,0:02:25.06,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,That's right! Except they stopped construction half a month ago!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.06,0:02:27.30,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Then we can play baseball in here?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.30,0:02:28.66,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.66,0:02:31.30,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,We can't get in here because it's locked,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.30,0:02:34.24,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,but I found another way in yesterday!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.24,0:02:35.57,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,This way!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.94,0:02:41.57,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}Geez...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.25,0:02:49.42,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Here it is!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.42,0:02:51.25,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,There's a hole!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.25,0:02:53.59,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Whoa! You broke it, Mitsuhiko{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.59,0:02:55.29,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,N-No!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.29,0:02:57.73,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,A car hit it.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.73,0:03:01.66,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,See? There's paint from a car on the fence.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.66,0:03:05.40,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,A car must've hit it and made this hole.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.40,0:03:07.60,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Alright! Let's check out the inside!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.60,0:03:09.87,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going in first!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.47,0:03:15.53,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,There's so much space!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.88,0:03:19.85,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,C'mon! Pull like you mean it!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.85,0:03:22.54,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}Go on a diet, geez!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.62,0:03:28.29,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Alright! This manhole will be the home plate!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.29,0:03:29.62,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm batter!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.62,0:03:30.86,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm pitcher!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.86,0:03:32.88,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm infielder!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.26,0:03:38.56,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Fine. I'll be outfielder.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.60,0:03:41.80,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Alright! Let's get started!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.80,0:03:43.08,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.08,0:03:44.04,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.04,0:03:47.88,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Conan{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}! I can't hear you!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.88,0:03:49.01,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.01,0:03:50.71,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,All right!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.71,0:03:52.81,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Here it comes, Genta{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.81,0:03:54.91,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Bring it on!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.89,0:04:03.16,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Conan{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}! It's headed your way!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.16,0:04:06.85,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}I'm just a ball-fetcher here...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.40,0:04:16.84,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}Still, this is clearly breaking and entering...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.84,0:04:20.54,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}If anyone sees us...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.34,0:04:22.54,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}What's that?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.78,0:04:31.55,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}Oh, crap! He's watching with binoculars!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.25,0:04:34.88,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Whoops!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.66,0:04:38.22,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It went over the fence...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.26,0:04:43.26,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't see the ball anywhere.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.26,0:04:47.17,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, could it have gone over that fence, too?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.17,0:04:50.34,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,That {\i1}is{\i0} quite possible.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.34,0:04:53.94,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Then let's ask the person who lives there to let us get it.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.94,0:04:57.01,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Good idea. Let's see...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.01,0:04:59.01,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,That seems to be a back entrance, so...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.01,0:05:01.88,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I think the front door was facing the main street.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.88,0:05:05.95,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,But what if a really stubborn man lives here?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.95,0:05:08.36,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know if he's stubborn or not,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.36,0:05:11.66,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,but someone was watching from the upstairs window with binoculars.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.66,0:05:12.59,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Binoculars?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.59,0:05:15.96,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Meaning someone is home, right?!\NLet's give it a shot!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.96,0:05:17.52,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Alright!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.71,0:05:27.31,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It probably flew into this yard.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.31,0:05:29.41,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It looks like a haunted house.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.41,0:05:33.21,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Why would a haunted house be right on a main street?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.55,0:05:40.45,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Conan{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.45,0:05:42.79,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,How do you read that?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.25,0:05:46.72,Dialogue Top,,0000,0000,0000,,"Yoshikazu Watanuki"
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.79,0:05:47.13,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh. Watanuki. Yoshikazu Watanuki.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.13,0:05:48.93,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.93,0:05:51.06,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I think he's coming out!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.54,0:05:57.37,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Whoa! He's scary!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.37,0:05:59.47,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,H-He's all yours, Conan!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.47,0:06:03.68,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Geez. You got a big body, but no guts at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.68,0:06:08.17,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Excuse me! Our ball landed in your yard! Could we get it?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.49,0:06:13.45,Signs,,0000,0000,0000,,Yoshikazu Watanuki (63)
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.92,0:06:13.69,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you students at Teitan Elementary?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.69,0:06:14.82,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.82,0:06:17.83,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,You're not allowed in my yard!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.83,0:06:20.49,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,That means leave!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.49,0:06:24.43,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,W-Wait, hold on! Without that ball, we can't...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.43,0:06:26.83,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,That's what you get for playing baseball there!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.83,0:06:31.87,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,If I catch you in there again, I'm contacting your school!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.87,0:06:34.20,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,You can't be serious...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.91,0:06:42.25,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,He wasn't a stubborn man. He was a stubborn {\i1}old{\i0} man.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.25,0:06:45.45,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,He could at least let us look around the yard!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.45,0:06:48.42,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn it! Give my ball back!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.42,0:06:49.86,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,There's nothing we can do.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.86,0:06:55.86,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Like he said, we're the ones at fault for going where we shouldn't.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.86,0:06:58.07,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Then it's Mitsuhiko's fault!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.07,0:06:59.67,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,You better pay for that ball!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.67,0:07:04.34,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! Let's forget about baseball and play video games at Conan's place!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.34,0:07:09.01,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Y-Yes, good idea! We can have some snacks there, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.01,0:07:09.91,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Boxed eel lunches?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.91,0:07:10.75,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.75,0:07:13.21,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! Don't decide things on your own!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.21,0:07:15.13,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Alright! Let's go to Conan's place!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.13,0:07:16.70,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes! Let's!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.03,0:07:28.60,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? There's someone there...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.60,0:07:31.67,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,So, there is. Is he a client?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.67,0:07:33.19,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Mister.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.04,0:07:37.17,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}He looks mean...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.17,0:07:40.78,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Did you come to the Mouri Detective Agency?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.78,0:07:42.08,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Who're you?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.08,0:07:45.53,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I live here! I'll show you the way!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.39,0:07:54.72,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm home!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.72,0:07:55.72,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Welcome back!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.72,0:07:57.06,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, hello!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.06,0:07:59.49,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Hello!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.49,0:08:02.43,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Not those pests again.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.43,0:08:04.60,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Mister! You have a visitor!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.60,0:08:05.93,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Visitor?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.10,0:08:12.61,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,My name is Koda. My younger sister went missing a month ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.61,0:08:15.94,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Now, now! Please have a seat first!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.94,0:08:17.92,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Ran! Make some tea!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.92,0:08:18.50,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Right!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.05,0:08:25.75,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry, but could you guys play outside a little while longer?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.75,0:08:27.56,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Bah. We have no luck.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.56,0:08:29.59,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.59,0:08:32.26,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,So, you want me to find a missing person?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.26,0:08:38.17,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,No. My sister was murdered! By a man named Yoshikazu Watanuki!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.17,0:08:39.57,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Watanuki?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.57,0:08:42.57,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,The Watanuki{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} who lives next to the construction site?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.57,0:08:43.64,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,You know him?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.64,0:08:47.24,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you kidding? We met him just now!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.24,0:08:51.08,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,He wouldn't let us get the ball Genta{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r} hit into his yard!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.08,0:08:54.75,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,He said, "You're not allowed in my yard!"
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.75,0:08:56.22,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Just as I thought!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.22,0:09:00.99,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,He didn't let you in the yard because my sister's body is buried there!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.99,0:09:05.13,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,H-Hold on! Please explain everything from the start.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.13,0:09:06.49,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Here you are!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.06,0:09:13.00,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I've seen him somewhere before!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.00,0:09:16.40,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,But I can't remember where from...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.40,0:09:19.57,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,My name is Masao Koda.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.18,0:09:24.14,Signs,,0000,0000,0000,,Masao Koda (29)
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.57,0:09:24.14,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I have just the one sister, and I was born in Saku, Nagano Prefecture.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.14,0:09:29.12,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, I know Saku! It has the Cosmos Road, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.12,0:09:32.82,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes. My sister loved cosmos flowers, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.82,0:09:35.59,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,This is my sister, Sanae.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.59,0:09:38.89,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh! She's very pretty!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.89,0:09:43.06,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,She really is! She looks nothing like her brother!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.16,0:09:44.12,Signs,,0000,0000,0000,,Sanae Koda (26)
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.06,0:09:45.27,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,She has white skin, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.27,0:09:47.37,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,You kids!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.37,0:09:52.71,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,My sister moved here six years ago\Nto work for Tohto Securities.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.71,0:09:58.08,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Two years ago, she became head of the Beika branch office.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.08,0:10:03.98,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,But on the night of the 8th of last month,\Nshe left to go see a client
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.98,0:10:06.25,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,and has been missing ever since.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.25,0:10:10.56,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,And this client was Yoshikazu Watanuki{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.56,0:10:12.13,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.13,0:10:16.00,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I came to town two nights after, on a Sunday,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.00,0:10:19.67,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,and learned about this at her office the following day.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.67,0:10:23.27,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Around what time did she leave the office?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.27,0:10:25.17,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Around 8:00 PM.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.17,0:10:29.01,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,She supposedly said she was going to stop by Watanuki's house
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.01,0:10:30.38,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,and then return home.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.38,0:10:33.31,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Why would she visit a client at such an hour?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.31,0:10:36.12,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,According to the branch manager,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.12,0:10:38.89,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,the stock Watanuki had bought had plummeted in value,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.89,0:10:42.96,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,and he was pressuring her into compensating him for his losses.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.96,0:10:46.56,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,One of those so-called "compensation payments," huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.56,0:10:50.76,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Did you go to see Watanuki{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}, then?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.76,0:10:54.97,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes. The branch manager and I went on the afternoon of the 11th.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.97,0:10:59.77,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,He says my sister never showed up the night of the 8th!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.77,0:11:05.61,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,But that's a lie! She went to his house that night, but refused to pay!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.61,0:11:10.21,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Watanuki snapped, killed her, and buried her in his yard!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.85,0:11:16.69,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Say. Why do you think she was buried in the yard?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.69,0:11:18.56,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,For two reasons.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.56,0:11:22.60,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,First, Watanuki doesn't have a driver's license.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.60,0:11:26.93,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,He couldn't take the body far away without a car.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.93,0:11:30.10,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Second, late that night, at about 2:00 AM,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.10,0:11:36.51,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,a businessman in the next house overheard a shovel digging.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.51,0:11:37.85,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Digging?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.85,0:11:40.81,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,A man named Mochida{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} who lives nearby.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.81,0:11:44.82,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,He says that construction was being done on the main street
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.82,0:11:47.29,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,that night between midnight and 3:00 AM.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.29,0:11:53.09,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Watanuki unquestionably used that sound to dig his hole unnoticed!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.09,0:11:57.00,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I see. So, did you tell the police about this?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.00,0:11:58.93,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Of course I did!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.93,0:12:02.97,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,But Mochida{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} had been very drunk that night,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.97,0:12:06.67,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,so the police said his testimony wasn't credible.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.67,0:12:12.98,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,In the end, they only questioned Watanuki on ceremony.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.98,0:12:19.75,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,He lives alone, and he's almost never left his house since that night.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.75,0:12:23.89,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,But every Saturday morning at around 10:00,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.89,0:12:28.53,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,he leaves for Beika Central Hospital\Nand is gone for two hours.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.53,0:12:31.07,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,So, Mouri{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.07,0:12:34.80,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Tomorrow is Saturday, so I'd like you\Nto come with me to his house
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.80,0:12:38.07,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,and deduce where he buried my sister's body!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.07,0:12:41.81,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll dig her up myself, of course!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.81,0:12:46.81,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,In other words, you want me\Nto sneak into his yard with you?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.81,0:12:47.85,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.85,0:12:50.95,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm afraid I can't.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.95,0:12:54.92,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It's illegal to enter others' yards without permission.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.92,0:12:59.93,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Besides, skilled as I am, it'd be impossible to tell, in such a short time,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.93,0:13:03.52,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,where a body was buried over a month ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.33,0:13:07.84,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Koda{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.84,0:13:10.00,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Very well.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.00,0:13:11.61,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Just forget it!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.61,0:13:13.20,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Koda{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.61,0:13:17.54,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry for bothering you.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.91,0:13:21.54,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Umm...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.29,0:13:26.95,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Now I remember!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.95,0:13:30.46,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,That person looks just like a Moletian!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.46,0:13:31.41,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Mole...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.41,0:13:32.66,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,...tien?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.66,0:13:33.50,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.50,0:13:35.43,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,He does, come to think of it!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.43,0:13:40.70,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Right?! Moletians take on friends' forms to trick Kamen Yaiba!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.70,0:13:44.64,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,They suddenly come out of the ground, just like moles!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.64,0:13:48.68,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh! So that's why he wanted to dig up the yard!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.68,0:13:51.61,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}Hey, now. That's not why at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.61,0:13:54.58,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you just going to let him go, Dad?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.58,0:13:59.22,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,What am I supposed to do? He told me to forget about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.22,0:14:05.63,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Besides, he's certain this Watanuki killed his sister and buried her,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.63,0:14:08.26,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,but there's no proof at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.26,0:14:13.20,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Even the shovel sound could've come from the street construction.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.20,0:14:15.34,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,That's true, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.34,0:14:18.97,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, I guess I can give it a quick check.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.97,0:14:22.84,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}Yeah, there is some truth to what the old guy says.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.84,0:14:25.28,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}We can't say anything for sure, at this stage...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.28,0:14:27.88,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Alright! It's decided!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.88,0:14:30.88,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's do it!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.88,0:14:33.05,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}I got a bad feeling about this...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.83,0:14:42.40,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}How did I know we'd be back here?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.40,0:14:46.80,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,First, we need to think of a way to get inside somehow.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.80,0:14:49.64,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,We can assume the gate is locked, so...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.64,0:14:51.23,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.57,0:14:54.01,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It's unlocked.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.01,0:14:56.64,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Lucky! He must've gone somewhere!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.64,0:14:58.41,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Alright! Now's our{\rHonorifics - Dialogue} chan{\r}ce!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.41,0:15:00.01,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,W-Wait, you guys!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.65,0:15:08.46,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, there's no way to tell where she's buried just by looking.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.46,0:15:13.29,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Of course not! We don't even know if she really is buried here!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.29,0:15:18.07,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Then let's start digging up the place! I'll go find a shovel!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.07,0:15:19.14,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait! Genta!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.14,0:15:20.86,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, you!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.46,0:15:29.88,Signs,,0000,0000,0000,,Beika Police Department
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.11,0:15:34.62,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, that Koda fellow gave us a bit of trouble, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.62,0:15:36.99,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,How so?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.99,0:15:41.06,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Watanuki{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} lost about 1.5 million yen in the stock market.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.06,0:15:45.49,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,That's a lot of money, but certainly not enough to kill someone over.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.49,0:15:46.93,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,That's true...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.93,0:15:51.00,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,On top of that, he's certain Watanuki{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} is responsible
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.00,0:15:54.34,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,and has been following him around for a month now.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.34,0:15:59.07,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,The way we see it, Watanuki{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} seems more like the victim here.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.45,0:16:10.02,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,We're sorry! We just really wanted our ball, so we snuck in...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.02,0:16:11.69,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,We're really sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.69,0:16:14.49,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,We're sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.49,0:16:21.43,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It's all right. I was a bit on edge before.\NI'm sorry I shouted at you.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.43,0:16:24.13,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I found your ball earlier.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.13,0:16:25.47,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll give it back,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.47,0:16:29.40,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,if you promise never to go\Nto those apartments to play again.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.40,0:16:31.77,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes! We promise!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.77,0:16:33.98,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Just a minute.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.98,0:16:34.92,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,This is great!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.92,0:16:35.53,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.65,0:16:40.20,Radio,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}One message.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.78,0:16:45.72,Radio,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}This is Beika Central Hospital.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.72,0:16:50.89,Radio,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}You have a checkup scheduled for tomorrow, so be sure to come.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.89,0:16:53.73,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, that sounded like...!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.73,0:16:58.77,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,What nonsense! I know that!\NI don't need to be told!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.77,0:17:00.17,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Here!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.44,0:17:05.47,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Now take it and get out of my sight!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.47,0:17:07.81,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,O-Okay...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.81,0:17:11.45,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,He was acting so nice at first,\Nbut suddenly grew angry.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.45,0:17:14.02,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,He's one moody old man, that's for sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.02,0:17:16.68,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! Did you hear that phone call?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.68,0:17:20.19,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah. It sounded a lot like Koda{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}'s voice.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.19,0:17:22.12,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Eh? Koda{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.12,0:17:24.29,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,You mean that Moletian?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.29,0:17:25.83,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,There's no question about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.83,0:17:28.03,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Koda{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} plans to dig up the body
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.03,0:17:31.69,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,while Watanuki{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} is at the hospital.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.67,0:17:38.41,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}But, is there really a body buried in this yard?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.41,0:17:45.21,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}Even if there is, it'd be impossible to tell where it is in just two hours.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.21,0:17:49.55,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}What exactly does Koda{\rHonorifics - Thoughts\be10}-san{\r\be10} plan to do?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.90,0:17:55.70,Signs,,0000,0000,0000,,The next day (Saturday)
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.56,0:18:02.50,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! Conan! What time is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.63,0:18:05.70,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Seven minutes to 10:00.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.70,0:18:08.30,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}Even after I told them {\i1}not{\i0} to come...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.30,0:18:10.94,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,That certainly is a big shovel!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.94,0:18:15.18,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I thought I'd help the Moletian dig up the body!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.18,0:18:17.95,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Say, what do {\i1}you{\i0} plan to do, Conan{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.95,0:18:21.52,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I intend to stop Koda{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} somehow.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.52,0:18:26.01,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Whatever the reason, sneaking onto others' property isn't right.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.69,0:18:34.06,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Mitsuhiko! Follow him!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.06,0:18:38.07,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,If he decides to come back, call us\Non your Detective Boys badge!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.07,0:18:40.19,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Right! Understood!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.48,0:18:50.24,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,What's taking the Moletian so long?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.24,0:18:52.91,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Conan. What time is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.91,0:18:55.21,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,10:10.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.35,0:19:02.22,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,That was Inspector Megure!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.89,0:19:05.99,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you think something happened?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.99,0:19:07.43,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll check it out!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.43,0:19:09.16,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! Conan!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.80,0:19:12.32,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Conan{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.70,0:19:18.67,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's have a look inside, Inspector.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.67,0:19:20.68,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Inspector Megure!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.68,0:19:22.58,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, Mouri{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.58,0:19:23.69,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Go on ahead.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.69,0:19:25.17,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.58,0:19:30.02,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I hear there was an armed robbery?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.02,0:19:34.12,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes. It took place about seven minutes ago and...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.12,0:19:37.66,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Does this mean you weren't here when it happened?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.66,0:19:41.83,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,No, I just happened to be passing by right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.83,0:19:43.87,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, I see!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.87,0:19:46.00,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I thought for sure you were at the scene of the crime, yet again...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.00,0:19:46.70,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Inspector!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.70,0:19:49.84,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,The security camera got a look at the robber's face!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.84,0:19:50.77,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Really?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.77,0:19:52.77,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,You know him too, Mouri{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.77,0:19:53.33,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.33,0:19:53.88,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.88,0:19:56.04,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Just come inside!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.62,0:20:07.29,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Inspector! Here he is!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.29,0:20:08.42,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It's him!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.42,0:20:11.05,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Just who is he, Mouri{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.53,0:20:14.46,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}Koda{\rHonorifics - Thoughts\be10}-san{\r\be10}!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.46,0:20:18.23,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,This man's name is Masao Koda!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.23,0:20:21.67,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,But why is he doing a jewel robbery?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.67,0:20:26.41,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Whatever the case, Koda ran off\Nwith a dozen or so jewels!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.41,0:20:27.64,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Inspector Megure!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.64,0:20:31.48,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,The robber's motorcycle\Nwas found near Beika Station!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.48,0:20:32.74,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,- What?!\N- What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.55,0:20:40.42,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,No doubt about it, Inspector.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.42,0:20:43.86,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,The plate number matches with the witness' testimony perfectly.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.86,0:20:45.39,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Inspector Megure!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.39,0:20:48.40,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,We found this on the station stairs!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.40,0:20:50.06,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,A jewel...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.06,0:20:54.47,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,No question about it! He got on the Loop Line from Beika Station!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.47,0:20:57.14,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I want emergency deployment at all stations on the Loop Line!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.14,0:20:58.21,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Understood!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.21,0:21:01.31,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone else, continue to scour the vicinity!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.31,0:21:02.18,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.18,0:21:08.88,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}Is Ayumi right? Has Koda{\rHonorifics - Thoughts\be10}-san{\r\be10} fooled us just like the Moletians?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.68,0:21:14.05,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}Was the whole story about his sister a fabrication?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.39,0:21:18.16,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}But why would he make that up?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.16,0:21:23.60,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}And, even if he had a reason,\Nwhy would someone so well-prepared
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.60,0:21:29.24,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}commit the crime without sunglasses or a mask to conceal himself
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.24,0:21:32.57,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}and ditch his getaway vehicle for everyone to see?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.58,0:21:44.59,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}A leaf? And it's fresh and green...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.59,0:21:50.69,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}The fact it's stuck here means someone opened this not so long ago!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.69,0:21:51.83,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}Wait a minute!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.83,0:21:54.76,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}There was one by Watanuki{\rHonorifics - Thoughts\be10}-san{\r\be10}'s back gate, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.53,0:22:02.37,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}Could it be?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.37,0:22:05.83,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}Is Koda{\rHonorifics - Thoughts\be10}-san{\r\be10}'s true objective...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:48.23,0:23:49.13,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It's him!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:49.13,0:23:52.43,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,He really is a Moletian!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:52.43,0:23:55.10,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Take me to 1st Street in Beika! Hurry!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:55.10,0:23:56.40,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,R-Right!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:56.40,0:23:59.34,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Genta{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}! The old man is taking a taxi back!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:59.34,0:24:04.51,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! Mister! Watanuki{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} is gonna be back soon!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:04.51,0:24:07.84,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}If my theory is correct, Koda{\rHonorifics - Thoughts\be10}-san{\r\be10} is...!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:08.07,0:24:13.99,Signs,,0000,0000,0000,,Next Conan:
Dialogue: 0,0:24:13.99,0:24:18.96,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Next Conan's Hint: Manhole
Dialogue: 0,0:24:19.23,0:24:21.45,Dialogue Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Next time, what's that hole Detective Takagi's digging?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:21.45,0:24:22.65,Dialogue Top,,0000,0000,0000,,A grave!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:22.65,0:24:23.89,Dialogue Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, dig away, dig away!
